    "summary": "LibTIFF 4.4.0 has an out-of-bounds write in `_TIFFmemset` in `libtiff/tif_unix.c:340` when called...",
    "details": "LibTIFF 4.4.0 has an out-of-bounds write in `_TIFFmemset` in `libtiff/tif_unix.c:340` when called from processCropSelections, `tools/tiffcrop.c:7619`, allowing attackers to cause a denial-of-service via a crafted tiff file. For users that compile libtiff from sources, the fix is available with commit 236b7191.",
